data.description: Welcome to your dream home on a corner lot in the heart of Texas City! This beautiful 4 bedroom and 2 bath house features a large, oversized living area with a wood burning fireplace.  Adjoining the living area, your kitchen has plenty of counterspace, perfect for preparing meals and hosting gatherings. The kitchen features granite countertops, modern appliances, custom wood cabinets, and a breakfast area, making cooking and entertaining a delight. The house also has 2 separate areas which can be used as a dining room, or a home office or study if desired.  You will enjoy 2 primary rooms with bathrooms attached, one with a walk-in shower and one with a double vanity sink and jetted tub. Huge fenced yard, with outdoor covered area perfect for entertaining guests or hosting gatherings. The house is situated in a great location with easy access to major highways and is just a few miles away from local shops and dining establishments.
